{"tid":2487576,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Webb轟限查冊：6個「陳志強」同ID組合","createTime":"2021-04-13T15:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:01:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74b8681199c47bc2e7ae64dd788b77123f1db600","tid":2487576,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/W4OKI4KFQ5GRFNOTNQT45D2MMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FW4OKI4KFQ5GRFNOTNQT45D2MMQ%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=36f51cb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210413%2FW4OKI4KFQ5GRFNOTNQT45D2MMQ%2F&h=38c991fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210413/W4OKI4KFQ5GRFNOTNQT45D2MMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\nWebb轟限查冊：6個「陳志強」同ID組合<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府即將收緊公司查冊，引起各界猛烈抨擊，尤其對董事資料「同名人士」的搜尋結果容易引起混淆，財經事務及庫務局長許正宇曾引數據反駁不會出現此情況，但獨立股評人David Webb（圖）作出實測、並批評政府誤導立法會。<br />\n<br />\n就政府收緊查冊措施，未來公司註冊處文件僅顯示身份證英文字母、首三位數字，以及隱藏居住地址，僅顯示通訊地址。許正宇上周五在立法會上指出，58.8萬名持香港身份證的香港公司董事中，只有八組人士的中英文全名及身份證英文字母、首三位數字相同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘆前年禁蒙面 今准董事隱身<br />\n<br />\n不過，David Webb引述2009年12月17日的諮詢文件，指「在香港不同人士擁有相同姓名相當普遍，限制身份證號碼將難以辨識個人身份，讓董事逃避責任及易於參與犯罪活動。掩藏三至四個身份證號碼難以識別個人身份，原因是不少人擁有相同名字而又擁有類似的身份證號碼」，他更引用一個普通的中文名「陳志強」（CHAN, CHI KEUNG），來證明四個身份證號碼顯示是如何不足夠。<br />\n<br />\n他在公司註冊處輸入「CHAN, CHI KEUNG」，得出245個董事紀錄，當中243位董事的身份證中第三位至五位數字被遮蓋，出現至少六組相同姓名及身份證的組合。進一步查冊發現，他們均是不同身份人士。當中一個組合的身份證號碼，只有第五位數字不同。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb促請立法會議員能夠關注上述例子，並要求許正宇提供真實數據。他更感嘆2019年時政府禁止人蒙面以能夠識別對方身份及罪行，今天卻求那些具有特權的董事隱身，助長罪行及貪污，要求暫停有關修例，並且取消公司註冊處收費制。<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局發言人昨。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J1oA_ygpfd1_AqkT3MznXRidwwc=/510x367/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SS4MTTEIPNBW7M7TYMUVL3HJTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ1oA_ygpfd1_AqkT3MznXRidwwc%3D%2F510x367%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSS4MTTEIPNBW7M7TYMUVL3HJTE.jpg&h=f079752c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71bd3fa3b78b7ee15dedc6a1e5661ba8fec29448","tid":2487576,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVZnWX7f7dnRGDNj9d17u5ZchHiuD3ZWta5DtEKBevRc2?filename=H2SZ2Ep.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2SZ2Ep.png&h=b84185e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00c02110703d77316a1654e419ffc7a4db3a6098","tid":2487576,"uid":85235,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:59:37.000Z","msg":"舉蒙面法做例子都幾好，証明政府立法只係為左保護奶共嘅人嘅權益<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f3095cdc0b2a58ea8a001bac57b7f0b8054dd0","tid":2487576,"uid":58880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:11:24.000Z","msg":"貪污唔驚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42034dd556eeea03e951c643a7ab8dcc535d53d7","tid":2487576,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71bd3fa3b78b7ee15dedc6a1e5661ba8fec29448","tid":2487576,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2SZ2Ep.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2SZ2Ep.png&h=b84185e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"有冇高清圖<br />\n睇唔清楚d 字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2372bae76aa7d42d15ee0ddc5007a3e9787c8723","tid":2487576,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c02110703d77316a1654e419ffc7a4db3a6098","tid":2487576,"uid":85235,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:59:37.000Z","msg":"舉蒙面法做例子都幾好，証明政府立